          <div class="links"><ul class="links inline"><li class="node_read_more first last"><a href="../../blog-posts/china-signs-paris-agreement-will-encourage-others-join" title="Read the rest of China Signs Paris Agreement, Will Encourage Others to Join.">Read more</a></li>
